				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${\varvec{P}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M26"><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold-italic">P</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12864_2022_8936_Article_IEq7.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula> is the probability of belonging in cluster <inline-formula id="IEq8"><alternatives><tex-math id="M27">\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
				\usepackage{wasysym} 
				\usepackage{amsfonts} 
				\usepackage{amssymb} 
				\usepackage{amsbsy}
				\usepackage{mathrsfs}
				\usepackage{upgreek}
				\setlength{\oddsidemargin}{-69pt}
				\begin{document}$${{\varvec{x}}}_{{\varvec{i}}}$$\end{document}</tex-math><mml:math id="M28"><mml:msub><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold-italic">x</mml:mi></mml:mrow><mml:mrow><mml:mi mathvariant="bold-italic">i</mml:mi></mml:mrow></mml:msub></mml:math><inline-graphic xlink:href="12864_2022_8936_Article_IEq8.gif"/></alternatives></inline-formula>. The lowest score of 0 occurs when all sequences are in a single cluster and non-clustered sequences are not included in the calculation.</p>
